    "sections": {
      "verse_A": "i-bVI7 alternation with V7 (C7) tonicizing i, closing ii( b5)-V into F minor",
      "verse_A1": "Same i-bVI7-V7 pattern in F minor with a chromatic dominant descent (Gb9-F9-E9) at the end",
      "verse_B": "Eb9(V7)-Ab(I)-Bb7(II7)-Eb7(V7) pivoting into Ab major",
      "A": "I with passing #i dim, V7 (Eb7), back to I, turnaround Bb7-Eb7",
      "A1": "I with #i dim, V7, resolving and staying on I",
      "B": "Dominant cycle C7-F7-Bb7-Eb7 (III7-VI7-II7-V7) driving back to I",
      "A2": "I with #i dim, V7, cadencing home to Ab"
    },
    "modulates": true,
    "modulation_note": "Verse opens in the relative minor (F minor) before the chorus settles firmly in Ab major."
